My general opinion is that I want communication and sharing, which means neither that people should trample each other on their ways to the big mobs, nor that I want a horrid ownership system like the one on SolRo. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ujzonn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jzonn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Newbie Poster</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/19/00 6:29:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://personal.bhm.bellsouth.net/bhm/r/p/rpo2/Jzonn_Icon.png WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Conesus--- FFA planes or schedule</span><hr size=1> I have no illusions about what it will be initially.  FFA.<br>
<br>
I hope there is enough contention to encourage at least a notification of intention for a target, but you'll always have someone who claims they never saw it (the intention notice).  It will really depend on which organizations actually manage to continuously get the big targets or clear the planes.  I know each server has some guilds which feel they can do this successfully. <p><B><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE=2 COLOR="#004080">Jzonn Stormwolf &lt;Unguilded&gt;</B></FONT><BR>
<I><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE=2 COLOR="#ffffff">Ranger of Karana</I></FONT></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uqalaar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qalaar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Newbie Poster</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/19/00 6:30:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Conesus--- FFA planes or schedule</span><hr size=1> I support a posted schedule.  But the number of days that can be spoken for in a row should be somewhat limited.  Five days is certainly too long for hate or fear, maybe not for air.  Two or three days seems more reasonable. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/urazorana.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Razorana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Newbie Poster</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/19/00 6:34:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Conesus--- FFA planes or schedule</span><hr size=1> FFA on planes, Schedule on saught after dragons such ass Trakanon, Naggy, Vox....  imho.<br>
<br>
Razorana Burnn<br>
Phantasmist<br>
Sphere of Trancendence <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ushadowcross.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shadowcross</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>AdminRogue</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/19/00 6:35:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.succubus.de/shadow6_sig.jpg border=0 heigth=123 width=80></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Conesus--- FFA planes or schedule</span><hr size=1> Any more than 2 days is totally crap.<br>
