 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/usanterre.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Santerre</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Newbie Poster</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/19/00 7:17:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Conesus--- FFA planes or schedule</span><hr size=1> Down with planes scheduling.  It was abused and never worked.  People need to use their heads and realize that sometimes you are going to have to share a plane.  You work together, maybe you will make some friends. <br>
<br>
Solusek Ro was at times a VERY nasty place.  If you moved, I suspect that is because you wanted a change.  Don't let it start here again, or you left a bunch of friends behind for nothing.<br>
<br>
A lot of planes-capable guilds moved from all three servers.  Be prepared to work together up there.  Generally, its more fun then bitching at each other.<br>
